                                                                                                                                Input and selection

                                                                                                                                Star rating

                                                                                                                                Stable

                                                                                                                                There are 2 types of star ratings: descriptive and interactive. Descriptive ratings are used to show data, such as the average ratings for a driver, rider, or restaurant. Interactive ratings allow the user to indicate how they feel about a product or service on a scale of 1 to 5.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Content
                                                                                                                                Spec
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog

                                                                                                                                TL;DR

                                                                                                                                • With descriptive star ratings, text accompanies the rating value to indicate what the rating is for. 

                                                                                                                                • Indicate whole-value ratings with the numeral and no decimal or trailing zero.

                                                                                                                                • Use a decimal and the value to 1 or 2 decimal places for fractional ratings. Don’t use a zero as the final numeral.

                                                                                                                                • Include the total number of ratings received, in parentheses, when the information is available.

                                                                                                                                • Express all feedback about service as a rating, not a review.

                                                                                                                                • In a sentence, omitting the word star from star rating is optional if the context is clear, but always omit the star icon. 

                                                                                                                                 

                                                                                                                                Descriptive ratings

                                                                                                                                Single-star ratings

                                                                                                                                A single rating shows a solid star supported by descriptive information before and after to provide context.

                                                                                                                                • Include the average rating value and the total number of ratings received in parentheses if it’s known. 

                                                                                                                                Do

                                                                                                                                Don't

                                                                                                                                4.2 ★

                                                                                                                                ★ 4.2

                                                                                                                                4.2 ★ (1,000 ratings)

                                                                                                                                4.2 (1,000 ratings)

                                                                                                                                • Always put the rating value before the single star, so the rating reads smoothly as 4.5 stars, for example.

                                                                                                                                Do

                                                                                                                                Don't

                                                                                                                                4 ★ (900+)

                                                                                                                                ★ 4 (900+)

                                                                                                                                • For whole-value ratings, use the numeral, with no decimal or trailing zeros. For fractional ratings, use a decimal and the value to 1 or 2 decimal places (don’t use a zero as a final numeral).

                                                                                                                                Do

                                                                                                                                Don't

                                                                                                                                4 ★

                                                                                                                                4.0 ★

                                                                                                                                4.2 ★ 

                                                                                                                                4.20 ★

                                                                                                                                4.75 ★


                                                                                                                                • In a sentence, omit the word star from star rating when the context is clear, and always leave out the star icon.

                                                                                                                                Do

                                                                                                                                Don't

                                                                                                                                Improve your 4.2 rating.

                                                                                                                                Improve your 4.2 ★ rating.

                                                                                                                                5-star ratings

                                                                                                                                These ratings show 5 stars, shaded to convey a rating value that has already been given.

                                                                                                                                Always include a short label that indicates what the rating is for.

                                                                                                                                Do

                                                                                                                                Don't

                                                                                                                                You rated Sean ★★★★★

                                                                                                                                Sean ★★★★★


                                                                                                                                Interactive ratings

                                                                                                                                Rate not review

                                                                                                                                Express all feedback about a service as a rating, not a review. This applies to rating riders, drivers, couriers, and restaurants. 

                                                                                                                                Do

                                                                                                                                Don't

                                                                                                                                How was your ride?

                                                                                                                                Review your ride

                                                                                                                                Rate restaurant

                                                                                                                                Review restaurant

                                                                                                                                Tell us your feedback

                                                                                                                                Review your experience

                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Use the word "rate," not "review," in the context of the rating component
                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Don't describe a rating as a "review"
